{
  "stem": "311.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm going to be here with just the Polack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then, I saw a guy, you know, who work-- he had-- he-- And I say, well, what's going on?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he says, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Your father is here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So what happened?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I went over to my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My father said, [NON-ENGLISH] you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So what-- what do you do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He say, well, I saw ghetto transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was on a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So he go, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Dad, don't rush.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just don't rush.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] And this was already [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just about four weeks before we went with Schindler.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see that only the people who left-- who were left over, most of it woman-- there were more.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there were mostly the people who they hold back so they can set up a Schindler camp, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, tell me, this was in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, this was in Plaszow, still?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Plaszow in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was Plaszow concentration.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what happened?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, [NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were looking for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] Ginter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Ginter was the man who-- who tried to get the mechanics.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He knew it, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How is he going to set up a shop, a factory, with doctors and lawyers and-- and professionals and millionaires and whatever, you know, people who never worked in their life, you know?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As he had.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he said, Shloyme, [NON-ENGLISH] OK, so he said, Shloyme, to your father--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, to my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was an electrical engineer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to give him jobs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, So he-- he knew it, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean he is in United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Matter of fact, I got once a job from Sweden, cash registers, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I see a guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
